::DarkMouse::

She looked at Terrorsaur. "Your lucky that your a bigger bot.  If 
Megatron hit you, you'd be able to stand up to it better than I. I'm 
lucky that he didn't hit me with a full force blow. I'd be just 
waking up by now if her had." She looked down for a moment and the 
looked at Drillbit.

"I'd just wait untill he's cooled off a bit before you go and talk to 
him.  He's interagating a prisoner right now. I'm just glad I'm not 
in her skin right now."
